\v 9 Umukwirwa ariisiriribhwa k Čbha mubhw…®ndi bhwa abhakwirwa, ar…®…®bh…® ani imyaka k Čtang…®ra merongo …®saasabha, naatu abh…® aar…® nu umusubh…® w Čmw…®.  
\v 10 Abh…® wu ubhukumya  Čbh Čz Čmu k Čmahocha gaaz…® amaz Čmu. Abh…® ar…®rir…® abhaana bhaaz…® bhwaheene, abh…® aginihiry…® abhagini, abh…® ah Čk…®…®ry…® abhiisirirya ko kobhooja amag Čr Č gaabh Č, abh…® abhasakiiry…® bhan Č bhak Čnyaakibhwa, na abh…® ak Črir…® amahocha g Č Čsi amaz Čmu. 
\p  
\v 11 Nawe abhakwirwa abhaacha,  Čtabhiisiririrya kusik…®ra mubhw…®ndi, k Č k Čbha …®namba y Č  Čm Čbh…®r…® …®rabhahiza k Čk…®ra kwihurucha kwa Kiriisit Č, bhayo bhareenda kukw…®rwa.  
\v 12 Muriyo bharabha bhiir…®…®t…®…®r…® z…®t…®n…®r Č, k Č k Čbha bhatigir…®  Čbh Črag…® bhwabh Č kwa Kiriisit Č bhw Č  Čk Čsaaga bhaguru.  
\v 13 Abhakwirwa ncha bhayo, bharanara eteemwa y Č  Čbh Čt Čbhu, bharagendagenda muzinyumba za abhaat Č. Kwik…®, bharabha bhagwatan ľya na bhariisikirya m Čmang ľana ga abhand…®, …®n Č bharagamba gan Č gatakwenderwa.  
\v 14 Mmbe, iny…® nereenda abhakwirwa abhaacha, bhabh…® bharakw…®rwa, bhiibh Čr…® abhaana na kwangar…®ra zinyumba zaabh Č, korereke abhabhisa bh…®…®t Č bhatatema amasoro.  
\v 15 Rora k Čbha abhand…® bhamarir…® k Čbh Čra na kutuna Sh…®taani. 
\p  
\v 16 Ar…®…®bh…®  Čm Čkari umwisirirya ana abhakwirwa mubhishoko bhyaz…®, abhasakiry…®. Akorebhu, korereke risengerero ritig…® kuhizwa, neho risengerero r…®rabha nu umweya gw Č  Čk Čsakirya abhakwirwa abhand…® bhan Č bhataana  Čbh Čsakirya. 
\p  
\v 17 Abhiimiiririri bhan Č bhakwangar…®ra risengerero bhwaheene, bhasuukw…® na kokorerwa amaz Čmu,\f + \fr 5:17 \fk Bhasuukw…® na kokorerwa amaz Čmu \ft kuKigiriki n…®‚ÄĎ\fqa bhasuukw…® manga kabh…®r…®.\f* k…®nda bhan Č bhakwihurucha kwerekeererya na kwija.  
\v 18 N…®rabhugabhu, k Č k Čbha yandikirw…® m ČMaand…®k Č Amar…®ndu, ‚ÄúEng ľombe han Č …®k Čh Č Čra …®ngan Č,  Čtayebhoha umunywa.‚ÄĚ\f + \fr 5:18a \xt Rora Amahiity Č gi Imigir Č 25:4.\f* Na yandikirw…®, ‚ÄúOmohocha areenderwa kurihwa ubhurihwa bhwaz…®.‚ÄĚ\f + \fr 5:18b \xt Ruuka 10:7.\f* 
\p  
\v 19 Utiisirirya  Čk Čgambwa kumwimiiririri wa risengerero,  Čk…®…®r…® k Čbha na bhomenyeekererya bhwa abhaat Č bhabh…®r…® hamw…® bhatat Č.\f + \fr 5:19 \xt Rora Amahiity Č gi Imigir Č 17:6, 19:15.\f* 
\v 20 Nawe abhiimiiririri bhan Č bhak Čkaja kokora  Čbh Čbh…®,  Čbhakany…® m Čbh Čtang…® bhwa bh Č Čsi, korereke na abhand…® bh Č Čbhah…®. 
\s1 Amaangirij Č kwa Timoseo 
\p  
\v 21 N…®rakuswaja m Čbh Čtang…® bhwa Mungu, na m Čbh Čtang…® bhwa Y…®…®su Kiriisit Č na bhamaraika abharobhorwa, ugwat…®r…®r…® gayo,  Čtat…®n…®ra kwa bhwang Č hamw…® k Čh…®ng…®r…®ra  Čr Čbhaara r Čmw…®.  
\v 22 Utiisirirya kwa bhwang Č k Čt Č Čr…®ra  Čm Č Čt Č amabhoko komeremo j Č …Ąm Čk Čr Č, k Č k Čbha  Čraat Č Čr…®  Čm Č Čt Č  Čm Čbh…® momeremo giyo, na naaw…®  Črabha ugwat…®…®n…® m Čbh Čbh…® bhwaz…®. Aw…® wiyangar…®r…®, korereke  Čsaag…® moronge. 
\p  
\v 23 K Čtang…®ra nangw…®n Č, aw…®  Čtanywa amanzi ageene, nawe  Čbh…®  Čranywa ni idivaayi\f + \fr 5:23 \fk Idivaayi\ft . K Čmarag…®r…®ra bh Čk Čng ľu, rora Ikiniibhasa.\f* hasuuhu, ig Čr Č wu ubhurw…®r…® bhwaz Č bhw…® …®nda na amarw…®r…® agand…® gan Č gak Čk Čnyaacha. 
